  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Season the sirloin steaks with salt and black pepper.",
    "Grill the sirloin steaks for 4-5 minutes per side, or until they reach an internal temperature of 130°F for medium-rare.",
    "While the steaks are grilling, char the onion and bell pepper on the grill.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the paella, cumin, coriander, and paprika to make a spice blend.",
    "Brush the grilled onion and bell pepper with olive oil and sprinkle with the spice blend.",
    "Once the steaks are cooked, let them rest for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "Serve the sliced sirloin steaks with the charred onion and bell pepper.",
    "Garnish with minced garlic and grated ginger.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
